Hi Tom,
If memory serves correctly 1955-59ish buses had just a body # behind the 
front seat.  This body # stamping according to "Progressive Refinments" was 
completely dropped from buses, & Cabriolets 6 AUG 1959.  28 AUG 1959 the body # was 
dropped from KG's.
